sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant P as Patient App
    participant AI as AIProvider (Cloud)
    participant W as Walrus
    participant S as Seal Keyservers
    participant C as SUI Move Contracts
    participant D as Doctor Viewer

    rect rgb(240,248,255)
    Note over P,C: Flow A — Record Creation
    P->>P: record audio + ASR
    P->>P: redactPII(transcript)
    P->>AI: summarize(redacted)
    AI-->>P: StructuredSummary
    P->>P: AES-encrypt(summary, data_key)
    P->>S: wrap(data_key, policy)
    S-->>P: seal_blob
    P->>W: put(ciphertext)
    W-->>P: blob_id
    P->>C: record_anchor::create_anchor(hash, blob_id, policy_id, hospital_id, ts)
    C-->>P: RecordCreated event + tx hash
    end

    rect rgb(255,248,240)
    Note over P,D: Flow B — Authorized Read
    P->>P: gen one_time_token, hash(token)
    P->>C: access_grant::issue_grant(record, token_hash, scope, ttl)
    C-->>P: AccessGrant (shared)
    P-->>D: QR { record_id, grant_id, token_preimage, blob_id }
    D->>C: access_grant::consume_grant(grant, token_preimage)
    C-->>S: GrantConsumed event
    D->>W: get(blob_id)
    W-->>D: ciphertext
    D->>S: unwrap(seal_blob)
    S-->>D: data_key (after policy check)
    D->>D: AES-decrypt → render (no download)
    end
